{
  "stem": "3475.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they wouldn't do it, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in one place, they sent the dogs after her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she got beat up-- bit, bit by the dogs something terrible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, we had to put compresses all over her arms and legs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because that woman had a few bulldogs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she sent them after my mother, although she pretended always to be a great friend and a, you know, a good customer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And she loved-- that she liked my mother and everything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But when it came to the crunch, it turned out what they really were, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And one reason the Polacks were, were interested in getting rid of the Jews is because when the Jew was sent out to concentration camp, they could come in and take over all their, their belongings, all their valuables.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They had a free hand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so that was one reason why, why this happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "As far as me being-- looking-- not looking Jewish, maybe it did help me in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Maybe if I looked really what the caricatures, you know, describe-- depict as Jewish, with long noses, and so far, maybe life would be even harder on me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I cannot-- I cannot say that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But I probably suffered as much as anybody, you know, regardless of my looks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But I also remember when they first grabbed us, when they were taking us through the Warsaw Ghetto to the Umschlagplatz, which was where they were gathering the Jews to send them to Majdanek and to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "As they were marching us, there were Polacks standing around and calling out all kinds of derogatory expressions like [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You know, it's good that they're taking you away.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
